appeng.api.storage.data

Interface IItemList<T extends IAEStack<T>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IItemContainer<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public interface IItemList<T extends IAEStack<T>>
extends IItemContainer<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Represents a list of items in AE. Don't Implement. Construct with - For items: AEApi.instance().storage().getStorageChannel( IItemStorageChannel.class).createList() - For fluids: AEApi.instance().storage().getStorageChannel( IFluidStorageChannel.class).createList() - Replace with the corresponding IStorageChannel type for non native channels
